Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照亮黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.87,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说 促使宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.87,0:00:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.64,0:00:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方 呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.09,0:00:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.19,0:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶为此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.86,0:00:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换取持续戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.50,0:00:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为命运而不知所措之\N叹息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.54,0:00:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因无法抹去的记忆\N而为爱颤抖着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照亮黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.46,0:01:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说促使得宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的坠天使们啊\N美丽的飞翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.17,0:01:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重毒鞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.78,0:01:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当个好孩子 不要乱动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了!\N左侧重钻机驾驶舱 射击预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.90,0:02:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.60,0:02:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压...数量增加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险!\N超重飞弹!全部发射!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等..怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离临界点1559点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.58,0:02:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法使用超重压力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.92,0:02:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战影座舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.49,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月镖射击预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.43,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重新月镖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.55,0:03:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力子能量到达临界值!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神...被解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第八话超重战场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为...为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当在合神中时\N绝对要遵从斗牙的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,个人任意的行动\N将会使全体人员陷入险境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好自律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这我也知道啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不!你根本不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.87,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在今天战斗中\N害超重神陷入危机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为某人被敌人吓得半死\N就拼命乱发射飞弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有吓得半死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.84,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那个时候还不是一样\N错失了出拳的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.41,0:04:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算替自己的失误开罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把责任归咎在我的操控上面吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你磨磨蹭蹭的\N我才出手帮你的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你该感激我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次不管怎么努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司还是没什么立场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.16,0:04:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 不管是考虑\N攻击力或重力子点数上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.27,0:04:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起飞弹 在当时\N最有效的攻击仍然是压力拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算敌人分离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在拳头的破坏力下\N仍足以贯穿目标的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是可以击败对方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 是英司少爷他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,判断错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不考虑太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你想让训练加倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.35,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.02,0:04:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是受到敌人攻击的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕不只是第二发拳击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.76,0:04:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连新月镖都无法使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司的潜力\N并不如大家想像的那么低
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.21,0:05:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了!斗牙是合神后\N超重神的头脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担任手脚的我们\N要是没有听从头脑指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任意行动的话\N不就错失获胜机会了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手脚?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是脚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.59,0:05:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么态度呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微有点女人样吧\N电钻女!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还敢说你这个脚丫男!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电钻女...\N脚丫男...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚丫男!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手指部分的板金剥落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重钻机的机体也歪七扭八
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.08,0:05:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤痕累累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.02,0:06:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家昨晚才通宵打蜡的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重机组跟超重皇组合...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.87,0:06:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是"合神"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,针对这些机体使用的\N驱动机系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及制御系统上面的\N高科技分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.01,0:06:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在已进行到第4级的阶段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如同您所见到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重机组跟EFA所使用的\N战斗用机械有着完全不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.19,0:06:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复数构造发电机组\N以及驱动系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 这些对一般的\N飞行器、战车而言并不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.80,0:06:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了合神的\N辅助动力跟驱动系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.03,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此那里并没有可以让超重神\N产生高输出动力的技术存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不谈装甲的材质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.94,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,构造上而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.87,0:06:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重机组不过是\N超重神的手脚罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能算是个零件组而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.35,0:07:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们制造出\N跟超重机组完全一样的机械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也完全打不赢外星异种的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得不错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照手上握有的资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以38比1的比例成功重现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的关键
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然就在这架超重皇上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.40,0:07:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么关于这架机体\N我们现在了解了多少?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过前些日子收到了\N很有意思的测量资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.81,0:07:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神进行战斗的范围区内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.02,0:07:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,观测到平时不可能发生的\N重力值急剧变化现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.79,0:07:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重力?...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是牛顿的苹果定律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.51,0:08:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合神中绝对要遵从斗牙的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,个人任意的行动\N将会使全体人员陷入险境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚丫男
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.54,0:08:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.91,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东东啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶!我也一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.69,0:08:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请用 斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急状况...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.24,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重机组的停机库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被士兵级的外星异种入侵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人出现在城内?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.89,0:09:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有搞错!\N是想叫我光溜溜的去作战吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.84,0:09:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武装女仆班立刻前往停机库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.51,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请动员所有人员\N集中抵抗外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点!快点!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.04,0:09:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好了!欠打的是外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量不要损伤到城堡喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.88,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.89,0:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的成员们\N跟武装女仆班合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.99,0:09:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各个击破城内的外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.36,0:09:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙 趴下!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情大条了啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有个万一\N我们也得加入战斗才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准它们踏进这个司令室一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.96,0:10:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城内竟然出现敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.43,0:10:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道这座城堡的所在位置\N已经被对方知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.57,0:10:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不过是在白天交战的外星异种\N有一部份在机库里再生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的增殖速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.84,0:10:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽快扫除机库内的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裘伊露 呼叫斗牙他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,入侵城堡内的\N外星异种本体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经控制了超重机组的停机库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑要第一优先\N彻底、迅速的清除掉所有在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.92,0:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通往超重皇停机库路线内\N出现的外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是没办法联络到英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.13,0:11:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那边有什么消息吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!他不在那边吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用G呼叫也没有回应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种紧急的时刻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司到底在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇 启动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙...及时赶到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开启连线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.78,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.22,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么情况啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子!你在那里干什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要突然对我大叫啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不行的啦!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上给我下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.94,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样英司?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.47,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能把现在在这个基地\N的外星异种全部消灭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.01,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以你跟超重皇的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.81,0:12:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以英司的能力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你行吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然!我当然行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司我们所有人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟这座城堡的命运\N就都交给你跟超重皇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.44,0:12:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对着那个\N巨大菱形的东西集中攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在它羽化前打倒它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.48,0:13:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.65,0:13:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.89,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些家伙\N我来当你们的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷文敌人的行动很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇在停机库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟被认为是主体的战士级\N外星异种交战中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵级的外星异种\N应该正赶往支援主体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.29,0:13:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等...你说超重皇...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在英司正在驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.78,0:14:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力量太大了\N实在不好控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.74,0:14:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且操纵起来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙一直在搞这种\N累死人的东西吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又变大了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像陷入危机了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷请您回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.29,0:14:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷\N去司令室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这玩意不赖!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你整成这副德性\N这是回敬你的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有效?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.01,0:16:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司 从那里撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.69,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算对着毁灭者级\N外星异种反覆攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也无法造成它的损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我撤退...\N我能撤到哪里去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.73,0:17:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样!\N先把能打倒这家伙的方法告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.07,0:17:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将手放在手臂握把前端的\N超重天球体上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等候桑德曼的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行!绝对不可以这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.68,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若没有重力子的力量\N是无法打倒它们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.55,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会消灭这家伙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.76,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说我也都上场啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.93,0:17:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工学型态时的超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.53,0:17:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会对搭乘者的肉体\N造成相当大的负担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.94,0:17:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.10,0:17:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢啦!看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那、那到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用工学型态...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们又没有进行合神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什会那么的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.09,0:18:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓工学型态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是超重皇\N实行重力子能量循环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.79,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让自己发挥\N原有力量的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实行工学型态时的超重皇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.37,0:19:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会呼应操纵者本身\N所拥有的G因子而成为一体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.27,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并且在同一时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重皇的机体周围\N会形成重力子力场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.01,0:19:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并诱发装备在机体上武器的潜能\N产生大幅度的提升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给予其压倒性的破坏力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.61,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会给予操纵者的肉体\N带来无比的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么所谓临界点又是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.10,0:19:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是超重机组可以抵挡\N重力子能量循环的界限值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而超重皇本身的临界点......\N不存在!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也该结束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丢出一些不可燃烧的垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人的身体却会有界限啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.73,0:20:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.69,0:21:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着在烈阳热气下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.30,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈现形形色色的摆动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.30,0:21:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该为何这般\N心头思绪纷乱不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就这么视而不见\N朝向明日飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.56,0:22:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.69,0:22:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才说出了这么不客气的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤单一人地强出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.93,0:22:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换来的只有误解\N矛盾与迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.84,0:22:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于那牵系着悲伤的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.11,0:22:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让微笑的双眸中渗出了泪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.55,0:22:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想将这暖意传送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.35,0:22:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便紧握着手一直不愿放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让这祈祷得以传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.43,0:22:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司让我告诉你\N你所不知道的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.00,0:22:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐请注意\N不要在城内发生不正常关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.97,0:22:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下回播出\N"遥远的拥抱"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.81,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周也将照料各位的和平!